Boon Water Bugs Bath Toy Price: Rs.525

One of the biggest reliefs for a mother would be if the kid looks forward to bath-time and enjoys it
column15: preventing her from the hassles of forcing him to get into the shower. Well
column17:
colourful and attractive Water Bugs from Boon almost accomplish fulfilling this purpose.

\r\n

\r\n\tThe pack consists of three bugs and a net
column18: which prove to be great for developing dexterity and an aptitude for Entomology in the kid. You can set these colourful insects free in the bath and watch your kids reach out for them as they glide across the water. The dimensions of these bugs are 12.7 x 20.32 x 5.08 cm and are very safe to use since they are BPA
column19:
Phthalate and PVC free. These bugs are most recommended for babies belonging to the age group of 9+ months as it makes the bath-time real fun for them.
